            "title": "半日收市︱科股領漲 恒指半日回升404點報20622點 小米、中芯齊破頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國暫緩對加拿大及墨西哥加徵關稅，中美兩國元首亦將通電，港股今早顯著揚升，小米(01810)與中芯(00981)均創歷史新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早高開271點後升勢迅速擴大，開市僅約1小時便衝上20885點半日高位，飆668點，其後由高位反覆回吐，但大部份時間仍在20600點之上；恒指中午收報20622點，升幅收窄至404點或2%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：遠洋集團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：遠洋集團官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數顯著跑贏，半日升185點或3.91%，報4922點；國企指數升190點或2.58%，報7574點。主板半日成交890.28億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升361點，報20683點，高水61點。科指期貨升173點，報4933點，高水10點。國指期貨升172點，報7597點，高水23點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股表現搶鏡，去年藍籌升幅排行榜首的小米，被摩根大通評為DeepSeek引發AI投資領域重直應用首選之一，股價今早初段曾突破40元大關，高見40.1元、升5.67%，市值一度衝破萬億元，其後升幅收窄；小米中午收報39.3元，仍升3.56%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同樣被摩通視為DeepSeek引發AI投資領域重直應用首選的騰訊(00700)與阿里巴巴(09988)，今早亦展現升勢。阿里巴巴經過昨天逆市揚升支撐大市後，今早再漲2.45%，報96.3元；騰訊也升2.82%，報415.6元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「ATMXJ」其餘兩隻股份更明顯領先大市，其中美團(03690)終於追落後，半日漲4.22%，報148.3元；京東(09618)走勢更凌厲，半日收漲5.27%，報159.9元。單是「ATMXJ」，已為恒指提供201點進賬。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯是另一隻今早破頂的重磅藍籌科股，升勢還遠勝小米。《紐約時報》早前報道指，中芯成功攻克5奈米製程核心技術，有關消息成為推動該股踏入蛇年後繼續領漲的主要原因。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯今早輕微高開0.72%後，未幾即顯著揚升，中段一度衝上45.7元，飆9.07%；該股中午收報44.75元，仍漲6.8%，在藍籌升幅榜上位居次席。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其餘芯片及半導體相關股亦借勢炒上，華虹半導體(01347)亦飆8.73%，報24.9元；上海復旦(01385)升7.39%，報15.4元；中電華大科技(00085)升7.2%，報1.34元。晶門半導體(02878)更漲10.42%，報0.53元；腦洞科技(02203)也升9.95%，報0.21元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">與此同時，尚有不少重磅科股價量齊升。聯想(00992)升6.5%，報10.48元，在藍籌升幅榜排第5位，半日成交達10.03億元；平台經濟股嗶哩嗶哩(09626)漲7.12%，報135.5元，在科技成分股升幅榜排第4位，半日成交也有4.28億元；快手(01024)升3.24%，報43元，成交9.47億元；金山雲(03896)升6.52%，報8.33元，成交5.93億元；美圖(01357)漲6.47%，報4.61元，成交3.2億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天受壓的車股今早大幅反彈，當中新能源車股升幅尤其明顯。理想汽車(02015)漲7.21%，報92.9元，登上藍籌升幅榜首；小鵬汽車(09868)則是表現最佳科指成分股，升12.58%，報65.8元；蔚來(09866)升3.61%，報34.45元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240312_FI_source-web_小鵬汽車.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小鵬汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地汽車龍頭股比亞迪(01211)也升3.86%，報285.2元；吉利汽車(00175)更漲6.63%，報15.76元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地消費股表現也絕未失禮，泡泡瑪特(09992)獲麥格理唱好，目標價達111元，該股今早即重越百元關口，中午收報100.2元，升8.15%。海底撈(06862)與李寧(02331)均齊上藍籌升幅榜前10名內，海底撈升5.14%，報14.74元；李寧升4.88%，報16.32元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：遠洋集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">異動股方面，遠洋集團(03377)英國債務重組計畫獲法院批准，該股今早曾彈36.36%，高見0.3元；中午收報0.249元，升幅收窄至13.18%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多隻盈警股今早齊齊逆市下滑，綠城中國(03900)跌1.78%，報8.3元；百果園(02411)跌3.28%，報1.18元；四環醫藥(00460)也跌3.45%，報0.56元。</p>\n</div>",
