        {
            "title": "港元拆息回升  惟按揭息率續跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息普遍回升，但與樓按相關的1個月拆息連跌3天，報3.7厘，較上日跌4點子，續創去年9月20日以來最低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241004_CR_SSP4_source-bp_.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241004_CR_SSP4_source-bp_.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜息升29基點至3.94476厘，1周拆息升至3.77673厘，反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息升至3.79857厘，6個月期微跌至3.88458厘，1年期升至3.92702厘。　</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">目前大型銀行H按息率全期H加1.3厘計，名義上H按按息5厘。以400萬元貸款額計，年期30年，按息5厘計算，業主每個月供款為21,473元。不過，現時「封頂息」普遍為3.5厘，故供樓人士最高供款為17,962元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14681063-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87-%e6%83%9f%e6%8c%89%e6%8f%ad%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e7%ba%8c%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230712-113850_202307_HK-View_15_source-bp__FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 12:00:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "DeepSeek已登陸騰訊、阿里巴巴及百度等雲服務",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地人工智能(AI)初創DeepSeek先後登陸騰訊(00700)、阿里巴巴(09988)和百度(09888)旗下的雲服務平台。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"DeepSeek (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250128_GL_source_AP_DeepSeek.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"DeepSeek (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250128_GL_source_AP_DeepSeek.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">DeepSeek (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊旗下騰訊雲公布，DeepSeek的DeepSeek-R1大模型已登陸騰訊雲的雲應用平台，用戶可通過一鍵安裝，4分鐘即可使用。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴旗下阿里雲及百度的百度智能雲，亦宣布上線DeepSeek大模型。阿里雲宣布，阿里雲PAI Model Gallery支持雲上一鍵部署DeepSeek-V3、DeepSeek-R1，用戶可以零代碼實現從訓練到部署再到推理的全過程，簡化模型開發流程。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度智能雲宣布，百度智能雲千帆平台已正式上架DeepSeek-R1和DeepSeek-V3模型，推出超低價格方案，以及限時免費服務。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">DeepSeek於去年12月上線並開源DeepSeek V3/ R1/Janus Pro，近期已有華為雲、騰訊雲、360數字安全、雲軸科技ZStack等多個平台宣布上線DeepSeek大模型。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海外方面，亞馬遜AWS、微軟Azure、輝達(Nvidia)等全球多間科企陸續宣布接入DeepSeek模型。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680835-deepseek%e5%b7%b2%e7%99%bb%e9%99%b8%e9%a8%b0%e8%a8%8a%e3%80%81%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%8f%8a%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6%e7%ad%89%e9%9b%b2%e6%9c%8d%e5%8b%99",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250128_GL_source_AP_DeepSeek_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 11:05:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股半日升逾600點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國推遲對加拿大及墨西哥加徵關稅，亞太區股市造好。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市半日升逾600點。日經指數半日收報39140點，升620點，升幅1.61%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680907-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be600%e9%bb%9e-2",
