        {
            "title": "阿里雲與百度智能雲相繼上線DeepSeek大模型",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">DeepSeek大受歡迎，阿里巴巴(09988)旗下阿里雲及百度(09888)的百度智能雲，亦宣布上線DeepSeek大模型。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里雲 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里雲 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里雲 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里雲宣布，阿里雲PAI Model Gallery支持雲上一鍵部署DeepSeek-V3、DeepSeek-R1，用戶可以零代碼實現從訓練到部署再到推理的全過程，簡化模型開發流程。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度智能雲宣布，百度智能雲千帆平台已正式上架DeepSeek-R1和DeepSeek-V3模型，推出超低價格方案，以及限時免費服務。今次接入的模型已全面融合千帆推理鏈路，集成百度獨家內容安全算子，實現模型安全增強與企業級高可用保障，同時支持完善的BLS日誌分析和BCM告警，助力用戶安全、穩定地構建智能應用。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在阿里雲與百度智能雲之前，華為雲、騰訊(00700)旗下騰訊雲、360數字安全、雲軸科技ZStack等多個平台，均已宣布上線DeepSeek大模型。亞馬遜AWS、微軟Azure、輝達(Nvidia)等全球多間科企，亦陸續宣布接入DeepSeek模型。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680809-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e9%9b%b2%e8%88%87%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e9%9b%b2%e7%9b%b8%e7%b9%bc%e4%b8%8a%e7%b7%9adeepseek%e5%a4%a7%e6%a8%a1%e5%9e%8b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250111_GL_source-ap_DeepSeek.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 10:30:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "遠洋集團曾升逾36%   英國債務重組計劃獲法院批准",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">遠洋集團(03377)境外債務重組獲批准，今早高開13.6%，報0.25元，最高報0.3元，急升36.4%，報0.3元，現升18.18%，報0.26元，成交2660萬股，涉資709萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遠洋集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230824_FI_source-web_遠洋集團1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：遠洋集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">遠洋集團昨晚公布，英格蘭法院於2025年2 月3日(倫敦時間)判決，集團英國重組計劃獲批准。集團早前公布境外債務重組，尋求批准英國重組計劃的申請1月15至20日期間進行聆訊。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團表示，將適時另行刊發公告，以知會有關重組的重大發展情況，包括重組計劃生效日期、香港協議安排生效日期及重組生效日期的發生。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680820-%e9%81%a0%e6%b4%8b%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be36-%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5%e5%8b%99%e9%87%8d%e7%b5%84%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83%e7%8d%b2%e6%b3%95%e9%99%a2%e6%89%b9%e5%87%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230814_FI_source-web_03377_SINO-OCEAN-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 10:30:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股升幅擴大 早前曾漲逾500點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">踏入蛇年第2個交易日，港股今早高開後升幅持續擴大，恒生指數開市後僅約40分鐘已曾升逾500點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-ap_00388.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-ap_00388.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約10時11分，恒指報20710點，仍升492點或2.44%；早前最高曾報20731點，升514點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股領漲，恒生科技指數升近4%。小米(01810)一度突破40元關口，曾衝上40.1元；於上午約11時13分報39.7元，仍漲4.61%。中芯(00981)亦創3年高位，報44.7元，升6.68%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680779-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%97%a9%e5%89%8d%e6%9b%be%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be500%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 10:20:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "SHEIN據報或遭歐盟調查是否遵守消費者法規",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》引述消息人士報道，歐盟或對SHEIN是否遵守消費者法規的問題，展開調查，SHEIN隨時面臨罰款。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/12/20241212_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/12/20241212_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市傳正申請於英國上市的內地快時尚電商平台SHEIN，可能遭歐盟調查。根據《彭博》的報道，歐盟委員會將領導成員國的消費者保護監管機構，對SHEIN採取協調行動，任何潛在罰款都將由各國政府決定。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道又指，之前拼多多及蘋果公司，亦曾因潛在違規行為面臨歐盟的類似行動。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680744-shein%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e6%88%96%e9%81%ad%e6%ad%90%e7%9b%9f%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5%e6%98%af%e5%90%a6%e9%81%b5%e5%ae%88%e6%b6%88%e8%b2%bb%e8%80%85%e6%b3%95%e8%a6%8f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/02/20240228_BLOG_-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 09:50:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段揚升 恒指回升271點報20488點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國關稅威脅或有轉機，亞洲外圍股市今早應聲反彈，港股亦高開。恒生指數開市報20488點，升271點或1.34%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：港交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：港交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：港交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報4828點，升91點或1.93%；國企指數以7499點開市，升115點或1.56%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍向好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報96.8元，升2.98%；騰訊(00700)開報409.2元，升1.24%；美團(03690)開報144.9元，升1.83%。滙控(00005)開報79.8元，逆市微跌0.13%；友邦(01299)開報54元，升1.03%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多家公司發盈警，其中百果園(02411)料去年由盈轉虧，該股今早開報1.2元，跌1.64%；綠城中國(03900)與四環醫藥(00460)於競價時段則暫無升跌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14680713-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87271%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b120488%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKS_source-bp_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-04 09:30:30",
